race.description: Spelling At Coolmore Mt White Handicap
race.comment: MASVINGO (6) sat off the fast tempo on resumption when a respectable third to her classy stablemate Paradoxium, over 1100m in the LR Wyong Magic Millions 2yo Classic. Well drawn again with fitness on her side. TIGRONI (8) impressive debut when covered ground from the outside gate to finish a game second over 1100m at Rosehill. Poorly drawn today but shapes as a top-three chance with race experience on her side. HALF PIPE (2) Extreme Warrior colt from Thurlow on debut for the Archibald yard. Impressed in two trials and can overcome the awkward draw. BY CHOICE (10) Written By filly from Audacious Choice on debut for the Waterhouse & Bott yard. Two good trial wins keep her in the mix.
